@startuml

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowThickness 1

[*] --> Unknown

Unknown --> Available : valid empty signal
Unknown --> Occupied : valid occupied signal

Available --> Occupied : vehicle detected
Occupied --> Available : vehicle leaves

Available --> Stale : no update within threshold
Occupied --> Stale : no update within threshold

Stale --> Available : valid empty signal received
Stale --> Occupied : valid occupied signal received
Stale --> Faulty : fault confirmed

Faulty --> Unknown : device reset / operator confirmation
Unknown --> [*]

@enduml